# Keep the Hugging Face Space build context (executive-ui/deploy/Dockerfile)
# small and free of stale local artifacts.
.git/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
executive-ui/web/node_modules/
executive-ui/web/dist/
executive-ui/dist/
**/tests/
# NOTE: do NOT exclude *.md — knowledge-base/ stores real data (opportunity
# profiles, VE-*.md experiment specs, recommendation briefs) as markdown.
